{
  "id": "adv_group_sun_03_02",
  "title": "サニーピース 03 02",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 4.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_02-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃんの夢を悪く言うなんて酷い！\nアイドルになりたいって思うのは素敵なことなのに！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's terrible‚ talking bad about Shizuku-chan's dream!\nWanting to be an idol is a wonderful thing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.4333345413
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_02-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃん……私のために怒ってくれるの……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura-chan… are you angry for me…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.4333345413,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.2475060462
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_02-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "当たり前だよ！　大事なお友達を悪く言われたら\n怒るに決まってるよ！　むぅ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course! I'm definitely going to be angry\nif someone talks bad about them! Hmph!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.5808393795,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.1141733486
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_02-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "中学時代の私にも、さくらちゃんみたいな友達がいたら\n少しは違ってたのかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I had a friend like Sakura-chan in middle school‚\nmaybe things would have been different…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.3952144681,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.2408634502
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_02-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃん？　中学で何かあったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku-chan? Did something happen in middle school?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.2408634502,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.0741909344
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_02-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "いろいろあった……けど、二人は聞かない方がいい……\nあまり気分のいい話じゃないから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A lot happened… but it's better if you don't hear about it…\nIt's not a very pleasant story…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.0802240689
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_02-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "言いたくないなら無理強いはしないけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you don't want to talk about it‚ I won't force you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.0802240689,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_02-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、そんな辛そうな顔見たらほっとけないよ\n嫌じゃなかったら、話を聞かせてもらえないかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I can't just leave you like this‚ looking so sad.\nIf you don't mind‚ could you tell us?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.9102252323
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_02-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "（二人とも、本気で心配してくれてる……）\n（私……そんなに辛そうな顔してた……？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（They're both… genuinely worried about me…）\n（Did I… really look that sad…?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.6919470151,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_02-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "（もしかして……本当は私も……）\n（誰かに話を聞いてほしかったのかな……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Maybe… actually‚ I…）\n（wanted to tell someone about it…?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.4586136818,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d_tokyoszkroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.9474146206
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_02-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "……分かった\nあんまり楽しい話じゃないけど……聞いてくれる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Okay.\nIt's not a very happy story‚ but… will you listen?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.5586136818,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.514693133
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.7480305353
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_02-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "（東京に住んでた私は、小中一貫校に通ってたから）\n（中学生になっても同級生の顔ぶれは変わらなかった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I lived in Tokyo and went to a combined elementary and middle school‚）\n（so even when I started middle school‚ I still had the same classmates.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.6919470151,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_02-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "（だから、私が書いた卒業文集の内容を）\n（みんな知ってて……よくからかわれてた……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（That's why everyone knew）\n（what I wrote in my graduation essay… and they often teased me about it…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.7252798398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "女子生徒A",
      "speakerNameEn": "Female",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "兵藤さんっていつもムスッとしてて雰囲気悪いよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hyodo is always frowning and brings the mood down.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.6196754772,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.6196754772
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "女子生徒A",
      "speakerNameEn": "Female",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "話し掛けてやった時くらい愛想笑いしろっての",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At least try to fake a smile when we talk to you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.6863431612,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "男子生徒A",
      "speakerNameEn": "Male",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あんな無愛想なくせにアイドルになりたいなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She's so unfriendly‚ yet she wants to be an idol?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.2530088106,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "男子生徒A",
      "speakerNameEn": "Male",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "冗談だろ？　世の中なめ過ぎ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What a joke! She's so naive.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.1196764945,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.5530149141
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_02-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "（人付き合いが苦手な私は、いつも独りで……）\n（陰口を無視して、みんなと距離を取ってた……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I'm not good at socializing‚ so I was always alone…）\n（I ignored their whispers and kept my distance from everyone…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.1586162249,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_02-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "（でも、完全に無視するなんて出来なくて……）\n（鏡で自分の顔を見るたびに、考えてた……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（But I couldn't completely ignore them…）\n（Every time I looked at my face in the mirror‚ I thought…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.2252828915,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.7448030153
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_02-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "私がアイドルなんて無理なんだ……\n笑顔、難しい……どうしたら笑えるのかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I could never be an idol…\nSmiling is so hard… How can I learn to smile…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.525288995,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8563.5952632,
          "startTime": 149.0888842582
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-night",
      "startTime": 148.5722165743
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-night",
      "startTime": 148.5722165743
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_02-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "（ある日、いつものようにライブを楽しんだ帰り道……）\n（私はドルオタ仲間とライブの話題で盛り上がってた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（One day‚ on my way home after enjoying a live as usual…）\n（I was excitedly talking about the live with my fellow otaku.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.6919546444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-night",
      "startTime": 159.4381127993
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_02-szk013.m4a",
      "text": "今日のセトリは神だった……！ 一曲目にあえての\nバラード……あれで世界観に引き込まれた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The setlist today was godly…! They started with a ballad‚ of all things…\nThat's what drew us into their world…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.6252879778,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_02-szk014.m4a",
      "text": "アンコールなんて、感動し過ぎて……\n泣きながら膝から崩れ落ちた……無理……限界……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The encore was so moving…\nI collapsed on my knees‚ crying… I can't… I'm at my limit…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.6586213111,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-night",
      "startTime": 172.5220927874
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_03_02-szk015.m4a",
      "text": "（ライブの感想を話し合えることが楽しくて……）\n（誰かに見られてるなんて思ってもいなくて……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Being able to discuss our thoughts on the live was so much fun…）\n（I didn't even think about the fact that someone might be watching…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.2919546444,
      "sfxList": [
        {
